7
00:00:50,890 --> 00:00:51,680
Right now?

8
00:00:53,770 --> 00:00:55,430
At school. Why?

9
00:00:55,910 --> 00:00:58,550
Oh... Nothing.

10
00:01:00,260 --> 00:01:01,410
I'll call you back later.

11
00:01:04,209 --> 00:01:05,090
