23
00:01:56,380 --> 00:01:57,530
Because they're talking about my man.

24
00:02:02,220 --> 00:02:03,410
Don't say what you don't mean.

25
00:02:06,430 --> 00:02:07,380
So,

26
00:02:07,930 --> 00:02:09,250
