27
00:02:11,190 --> 00:02:12,990
To get what I missed out on.

28
00:02:13,670 --> 00:02:14,550
What you missed out on?

29
00:02:15,260 --> 00:02:16,350
You know it best.

30
00:02:17,550 --> 00:02:20,820
