34
00:02:30,700 --> 00:02:32,520
Seriously, must you be so cold?

35
00:02:34,180 --> 00:02:35,460
We were once lovers after all.

36
00:02:38,750 --> 00:02:40,150
I contacted Jung Da-on.

37
00:02:41,230 --> 00:02:43,890
He totally ignored all my calls and texts.

38
00:02:44,450 --> 00:02:45,680
He really doesn't change.

39
00:02:47,290 --> 00:02:50,050
He always knows how to get me riled up.

40
00:02:50,480 --> 00:02:51,360
Kim Soohyun.

41
00:02:52,850 --> 00:02:54,290
Stop bothering Da-on.

42
00:02:54,600 --> 00:02:56,700
Why? Are you jealous?

43
00:02:58,400 --> 00:03:00,340
If you're jealous, be my boyfriend again.

44
00:03:03,580 --> 00:03:04,590
Bye.

45
00:03:10,290 --> 00:03:11,630
When I call you, pick up right away.

46
00:03:12,810 --> 00:03:14,210
Don't piss me off.

47
00:03:27,640 --> 00:03:28,470
Actually, earlier...

48
00:03:34,050 --> 00:03:35,210
Did you meet Kim Soohyun...

49
00:04:04,430 --> 00:04:06,160
[Alarm]

50
00:04:19,339 --> 00:04:20,779
Gosh, I don't want to go to work.

51
00:04:52,740 --> 00:04:53,450
Mr. Jung.

52
00:04:54,580 --> 00:04:55,480
Good morning.

53
00:04:56,470 --> 00:04:57,310
Yes.

54
00:04:57,600 --> 00:04:58,810
Did you get home safely yesterday?

55
00:05:00,110 --> 00:05:00,980
Yes.

56
00:05:02,630 --> 00:05:04,380
I did it the way you taught me yesterday.

57
00:05:05,200 --> 00:05:06,650
It looks better.

58
00:05:07,480 --> 00:05:08,610
Isn't it better than yesterday?

59
00:05:09,730 --> 00:05:11,950
Uh... Yes.

60
00:05:20,240 --> 00:05:21,130
Did I do it wrong again?

61
00:05:28,720 --> 00:05:31,900
[Meeting Room]

62
00:05:34,790 --> 00:05:35,890
[Da-on:
Did you meet Jaemin yesterday?]

63
00:05:36,100 --> 00:05:41,890
[010-678-308:
Jung Da-on, I'm in Korea. Pick up the phone while I'm being nice.
Don't tell me you still like Shin Jaemin? Don't piss me off. Pick up the phone.]

64
00:05:37,080 --> 00:05:38,180
[Da-on:
Don't tell me you two...]

65
00:05:45,790 --> 00:05:48,110
[Da-on:
Then do you want to have a late dinner with me?]

66
00:05:46,090 --> 00:05:48,130
[Da-on: I think I'll end late.]
[Jaemin: I'll be in school till late today too.]

67
00:05:55,280 --> 00:05:56,190
Mr. Jung.

68
