Yes?

69
00:05:58,150 --> 00:06:00,590
I just checked the material. There's no problem.

70
00:06:01,330 --> 00:06:03,350
After the examination, you can add it to the list.

71
00:06:05,090 --> 00:06:06,650
Send it to me by tonight,

72
00:06:07,300 --> 00:06:08,360
