73
00:06:09,100 --> 00:06:10,170
If you're done, let's go.

74
00:06:16,530 --> 00:06:17,350
Mr. Jung.

75
00:06:17,780 --> 00:06:19,570
-Let's have dinner...
-I have no appetite.

76
00:06:21,090 --> 00:06:22,900
-Enjoy your meal.
-Sorry?

77
00:06:26,030 --> 00:06:27,560
Oh... Okay.

78
00:06:29,130 --> 00:06:32,310
[Albi Construction
Strategic Planning HQ]

79
00:06:40,330 --> 00:06:42,060
He's been looking down since yesterday.

80
00:06:43,370 --> 00:06:44,290
Is something troubling him?

81
00:06:48,290 --> 00:06:49,640
But he should still eat.

82
00:06:51,550 --> 00:06:52,330
Mr. Ju.

83
00:06:52,860 --> 00:06:53,920
Is Mr. Jung out on business?

84
00:06:54,730 --> 00:06:55,590
Out on business?

85
00:06:55,590 --> 00:06:57,320
He hasn't been looking well,

86
00:06:57,320 --> 00:06:58,890
